headline: Distribution Solutions Group (DSGR) Lags Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: Distribution Solutions (DSGR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.78% and +1.77%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Jacobs Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of Jacobs (NYSE:J) has declared a quarterly cash dividend payable to shareholders in the amount of $0.32 per share of Jacobs common stock. This dividend will be paid on Sept. 19, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on Aug. 22, 2025.
